The former senator representing Kaduna Central Senatorial District, Senator Shehu Sani has taken to his verified Twitter page to react to a viral video of a lady that slept with a dog.
Recall that there was a trending video of a Nigerian lady seen in a TikTok video claiming she slept with a dog for N1.7million. It was gathered that the video sparked a lot of reactions from many people who condemn her action.
While reacting to the viral video of the Nigerian lady, the governorship aspirant and human rights activist, Shehu Sani who condemned what the lady had with the dog said it was immoral for human beings to sleep with a dog.
More so, he said it’s even immoral for human beings to be imitating the way of a dog while sleeping as well.
In his conclusion, Shehu Sani said everyone involve, including the lady, deserves serious punishment.
